# pi-soul-agent — docs index (git-notes)
#
# Design docs for this repo live in git NOTES, not the working tree — one ref
# per area of concern, all anchored to the ROOT commit. This note is the manifest.
# Skill: docs-in-git-notes.
#
# Read an area:   ROOT=$(git rev-list --max-parents=0 HEAD | tail -1)
#                 git notes --ref=<ref> show $ROOT
# Refspec (once): git config --add remote.origin.fetch '+refs/notes/*:refs/notes/*'
#                 git fetch origin '+refs/notes/*:refs/notes/*'

| Area         | Ref                          | Contents                                                                                  |
| ------------ | ---------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Domain       | refs/notes/docs-domain       | CONTEXT.md — ubiquitous language / glossary                                               |
